item.title: [HBASE-6876] Clean up WARNs and log messages around startup
item.description: I was looking at our startup messages and some of the 'normal' messages are a bit frightening at face value.
item.summary: Clean up WARNs and log messages around startup

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are closed can be reopened.

comments.comment:
